column5: Nice fish Matt.  Congrats on a great day
Thanks all.  I am still pretty stoked about the fattie, it was noticeably heavy lifting out of the net.  I'm going out tomorrow night for some dusk fatties, and hopefully another pic .....or three
now that's one wide-bodied fish-nice!
Wow!! I wish i could find one like that on stoney lk
awsome fish sounds like a sweet day on the water wtg
What a beauty.  I know someone who would pass it off as a 50 especially with the exagerating hold.

I have never targeted musky, but I am wondering why they say that musky are so hard to catch, I seem to get far to many when im out Bass fishing,its amasing how a fish that big eats little crank baits, and boy whats up with the smell
I don't think that was called for, Richard. Matt caught a great big fatty, let's just be happy at his success without slinging arrows at anyone.
.......shoots himself in the foot again
N-I-C-E F-I-S-H.........!!!!!!!!   right on matt,great looking muskie,nice job bud....cheers
Matt's a good friend and I can take a shot at him anytime I want.  Right Gord?
and who is that?
If I admit that will I be banned from OFC ...LOL  just kidding.  Yes bud friendly razzing is expected  And I'm not Gord ....you are  Now go fish....

Matt you really are hitting them this year.  Is there something different this year?  I dont remember seeing so many reports from you or others last year with the kind of success you are having this year.  Is it because the water stayed cooler longer?  Regardless you have caught some really beautiful skis so far this year and congrats again on finally getting the 50 in. you have been after.  Hopefully we can get out soon.  Take care  Don
Matt is keeping his drags tight
Bwahahhahaha......  Jamie you freekin clown..hahahaha  tooooo funny....  Thanks for the laugh
So thats the secret!
Man .. she is a fatty for only 45.   One very nice fish there.   Congrats.
Great fish Matt!
Wow Matt, impressive fish, lots of girth.  Joey
Lovely!!!
Great fish Matt. Congrats  you had quite the successful day, way to go  Mike
zoinks! thats one heck of a healthy looking fish!
Hope to hold something that big one day.MTP
It's all about the GIRTH. WTG.
Whoa!, I'll say that was a pretty awesome day! Congrats.
Matt Beauty ski man!!!
wow, great fish congrats
I can only dream....
Clean looking fishie, Bud...WTG!
Definately a big fish, I imagine the fight would be incredible. Care to share what lure you you were using? Trolling I'm guesing.
Very nice healthy fish WTG  Aaron
Thats a beautiful fish to top of what sounds like was a great outing!  Geeze, I gotta get up there and try the mighty Ottawa... Sounds like the place to be lately
What a beauty, very impressive!
Wow...one day I hope to be able to fight a fish that big...let alone land the thing!!! Great job!
WOW!  Great catch!  Forget about using poodles for bait...Looks like I'll be using great danes from now on...Swim Marmaduke, swim!
very nice!
beauty!
Wow... nice fish
Very nice.  Cheers Marc
NICE!! She's a fatty, gotta love those chunky fish!! You have sore arms today??
